            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516706",
        "quote": "Thanks to former President George W. Bush - remember the compassionate conservative? - I have a good name for the fundamental principle that should guide the Democratic alternative: compassionate deficit reduction.",
