                "url": "/topics/conservative"
            },
            {
                "name": "Principle",
                "url": "/topics/principle"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516707",
        "quote": "President Obama has repeatedly urged Congress to let the Bush tax cuts expire for those earning more than $250,000 a year. Increasing rates on top earners is an obvious way to raise revenue from those who can afford it most.",
