    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516708",
        "quote": "The central question is whether Medicare and Medicaid should remain entitlement programs guaranteeing a certain amount of care, as Democrats believe, or become defined contribution programs in which federal spending is capped, as Republicans suggest.",
