        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516710",
        "quote": "The most effective way to shake an economy out of a terrible downturn when we're at the zero lower bound is an aggressive change in policy that makes people wake up, say 'this is a new day' and change their expectations.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Christina Romer",
            "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516710"
