                "url": "/topics/downturn"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516697",
        "quote": "Recovery measures work better when they raise confidence - as Franklin D. Roosevelt understood. His fireside chats, and his inaugural address proclaiming he would fight the Great Depression with the same resolve he would muster against a foreign foe, were aimed at reassuring Americans.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Christina Romer",
            "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516697"
