    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_412061",
        "quote": "Where we're coming down is we currently have $787 billion of stimulus that's been passed. We're certainly focusing on spending that money as quickly and as efficiently and as transparently as we can. We think that's absolutely the right strategy.",
