    {
        "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516690",
        "quote": "If every other store in town is paying workers $9 an hour, one offering $8 will find it hard to hire anyone - perhaps not when unemployment is high, but certainly in normal times. Robust competition is a powerful force helping to ensure that workers are paid what they contribute to their employers' bottom lines.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Christina Romer",
            "url": "/quotes/christina_romer_516690"
